en_46646_0	Major General N.D Wanniarachchi, the newly-appointed 29th Adjutant General at the Army Headquarters assumed Office this morning (16) in a simple ceremony.
en_46646_1	Major General Wanniarachchi after observance of religious rites placed his signature in an official document to symbolize his acceptance of the new office at the Army Headquarters.
en_46646_2	Staff Officers in the Adjutant General Branch, Commanding Officer at the Army Headquarters and a few more senior Officers were present during the occasion.
en_46646_3	Before this new appointment, he served as the General Officer Commanding of the 12 Division at Hambantota.
en_46646_4	He succeeds Major General Shavendra Silva who is now the Chief of Staff at the Army Headquarters.
